# .gitignore für Power BI PBIP + Azure DevOps

## Power BI PBIP Secrets & Temp Files
*.pbix                          # Desktop Dateien (nicht in Git!)
*.pbit                          # Templates
~*.pbix                         # Locks
.pbi/                           # PBI Desktop Cache

## Credentials & Sensitive Data
**/.platform_secrets            # Nicht committed!
**/connectionStrings.json       # DB Credentials
**/*.credentials                # API Keys
**/*.env                        # Environment Variables
**/appsettings.*.json           # Secrets
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

## PBI Desktop Runtime
.pbidesktop/
.*_temp
*.tmp
cache/

## Azure/Fabric Authentifizierung
**/*.PublishSettings
**/PublishSettings.json
**/local.settings.json

## IDE & Editor
.vscode/settings.json           # User settings (optional)
.vscode/extensions/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

## Python Cache (für Validierungs-Skripte)
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
venv/
env/
.venv

## Node/npm (falls Web-Komponenten)
node_modules/
package-lock.json
.npm

## Build Outputs
bin/
obj/
dist/
build/

## Test Outputs
.pytest_cache/
coverage/
test-results/

## OS Specific
Thumbs.db
.AppleDouble

## DevOps / CI Artifacts (lokal, nicht im Repo)
.agent/
.temp/
.reports/

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## PBIP Project Backups (außer aktive)
**/*.backup.SemanticModel/
**/*.bak/
**/*.old/

## Template-Backups (ggf. in separatem Branch)
TEMPLATE_BACKUP_*

## User-spezifische Parameter (jeder Nutzer hat eigene!)
00_KONFIGURATION/parameters.local.md
00_KONFIGURATION/*.local.*

## Optional: Große Binärdateien (falls externe Daten)
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.parquet
# Uncomment wenn Daten committed werden sollen:
# !outputs/*.csv
